heading: Validity not subject to challenge in enforcement proceeding
text:
In any proceedings to enforce or discharge a lien
   created pursuant to this section 28-112.9 the validity of the lien shall not be subject to challenge based on:
      1. The lawfulness of the inspection, reinspection, examination, service or permit; or
      2. The propriety and accuracy of the fee for which a lien is claimed, except as provided in this section 28-112.9.
